{
  "page": "Tourney at King's Landing on the anniversary of the king's coronation",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>tourney at King's Landing on the anniversary of the king's coronation</b> was held in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, near the end of <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_58_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">58&#160;AC</a>, to celebrate King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>'s first decade of rule.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#The_Joust\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Joust</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Attendees\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Attendees</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_King%27s_Landing_on_the_anniversary_of_the_king%27s_coronation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The tourney was held at King's Landing in celebration of the first decade of <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>'s reign. King Jaehaerys watched the jousts in the royal box with his wife, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a>, and their children, <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen (daughter of Jaehaerys I)\">Daenerys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Aemon</a> and the newborn <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon</a>. The young knight, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a>, was the champion, and crowned Queen Alysanne as the <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_love_and_beauty\" title=\"Queen of love and beauty\">queen of love and beauty</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_King%27s_Landing_on_the_anniversary_of_the_king%27s_coronation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/32px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/48px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/64px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnal_Baratheon\" title=\"Ronnal Baratheon\">Ronnal Baratheon</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\"><img alt=\"House Oakheart.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/32px-House_Oakheart.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/48px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/64px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthor_Oakheart\" title=\"Arthor Oakheart\">Arthor Oakheart</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hogg\" title=\"House Hogg\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harys_Hogg\" title=\"Harys Hogg\">Harys Hogg</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dondarrion\" title=\"House Dondarrion\"><img alt=\"House Dondarrion.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/32px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/48px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/64px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Dondarrion\" title=\"Simon Dondarrion\">Simon Dondarrion</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/32px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/48px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/64px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lorence_Roxton\" title=\"Lorence Roxton\">Lorence Roxton</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/32px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/48px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/64px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lucamore_Strong\" title=\"Lucamore Strong\">Lucamore Strong</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Attendees\">Attendees</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_King%27s_Landing_on_the_anniversary_of_the_king%27s_coronation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Attendees\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>All the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Houses\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Great Houses\">Great Houses</a> attended the tourney, except for Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_Stark\" title=\"Alaric Stark\">Alaric Stark</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, who sent his two sons and his daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Alarra_Stark\" title=\"Alarra Stark\">Alarra Stark</a>, in his stead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd63.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd63.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Known attendees were:<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Boremund_Baratheon\" title=\"Boremund Baratheon\">Boremund Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Jocelyn_Baratheon\" title=\"Jocelyn Baratheon\">Jocelyn Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/20px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/40px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Lannister\" title=\"Lyman Lannister\">Lyman Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\"><img alt=\"House Velaryon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/20px-House_Velaryon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/30px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/